---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Vintage Wedding Invitations | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Vintage wedding invitation suites inspired by timeless typography, romantic details, antique design, classic layouts, and elegant wedding stationery.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Vintage Wedding Invitations</h1>

    <p>
      Timeless typography, romantic details, antique-inspired layouts, and classic
      design elements. Our vintage wedding invitation suites are inspired by old-world
      romance, elegant stationery, heirloom details, and nostalgic wedding design.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a historic estate wedding, romantic garden celebration,
      classic ballroom reception, or intimate vintage-inspired event, these invitation
      suites are designed to feel refined, personal, and timeless.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Timeless Wedding Design</h2>

    <p>
      Vintage weddings are loved for their sense of character, romance, and history.
      These invitation suites often feature elegant serif typography, delicate borders,
      soft color palettes, antique details, script lettering, archival-inspired layouts,
      and refined paper goods.
    </p>

    <p>
      Popular wedding venues and settings for this style include historic estates,
      garden venues, ballrooms, private clubs, museums, vineyards, and destination
      weddings with old-world charm.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Vintage Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Classic vintage wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Old-world wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>Romantic script wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Antique-inspired wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Garden vintage wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Elegant estate wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Timeless black and white wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Heirloom-style wedding paper goods</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Romantic, Elegant Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Our vintage invitation suites are created for couples who want wedding stationery
      with warmth, character, and timeless appeal. Each suite can include save the dates,
      wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, welcome signage, menus,
      seating charts, and day-of wedding stationery.
    </p>

    <p>
      We focus on cohesive wedding branding that feels classic, polished, and connected
      across every printed and digital detail.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Vintage Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for a fully custom vintage design? We can create personalized invitation
      suites inspired by your venue, wedding colors, typography preferences, family
      details, artwork inspiration, and overall wedding aesthetic.
    </p>

    <p>
      From romantic old-world designs to clean classic layouts, we help create wedding
      stationery that feels meaningful and beautifully designed.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>What is a vintage wedding invitation style?</h3>
    <p>
      Vintage wedding invitations are inspired by classic stationery, antique design,
      romantic typography, historic details, and timeless layouts. The style can feel
      elegant, nostalgic, formal, or softly romantic.
    </p>

    <h3>Can vintage wedding invitations still feel modern?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Vintage-inspired designs can be paired with clean layouts, modern spacing,
      and updated color palettes for a refined look that feels current and timeless.
    </p>

    <h3>Are the invitation suites customizable?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Colors, fonts, layouts, wording, paper details, and matching stationery
      pieces can all be customized.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding signage and day-of paper goods?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching welcome signs, menus, seating charts, place cards, and other
      day-of stationery can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
